### Middleware & routing

- Use `frontend/middleware.ts` to protect routes and enforce auth
- Organize routes using groups like `(auth)` and `(chat)` in `frontend/app`

### Auth UX

- Tokens in HTTP-only cookies; fetch with `credentials: 'include'`
- Redirect unauthenticated users to sign-in

